svg.text: Veteran starts initial liability claim for a medical condition via MyService
Veteran enters free text name of condition and onset date
Service history in MyService is complete already
MyService requests data about recognised operations (names and dates)
SoP API provides operations data based on current law
MyService sends veteran's description of condition to SoP API
SoP API attempts to identify correct condition name
* accept the claim under the RH standard
* accept the claim under the BoP standard, or
MyService notifies veteran of outcome immediately
SoP API provides factors for that
standard of proof for the condition
